data.description: NOW OFFERING $5000 TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS! The Highlands is an award-winning community. Why wait for new construction when you can make this home built in 2021 yours sooner! This 3010 sq ft home is located in a cul-de-sac and has 4 bdrms, 3.5 baths. The exterior opens to a spacious foyer that includes French doors leading to a light-filled room that can be used as a library or office. The kitchen/dining/living space is open concept, with light gray LVP flooring and views of the fenced-in backyard.  The kitchen boasts a HUGE island w/seating & pendant lighting, SS appliances, recessed lighting, and a large pantry. Off the family room is a private office that could be used as a first-floor bdrm—perfect for out-of-town guests. Upstairs, a loft makes an ideal hang-out spot for watching movies or relaxing with a good book. The primary bedroom has a vast layout, and features his and hers walk-in closets, and an ensuite bath with double vanities and private toilet closet. There is a 2nd bedroom with full ensuite bath, plus 2 more bedrooms, another full bath, and a large laundry room on this level. This home also has a 2-car garage and irrigation system. Schedule an appointment today!
